<p class="cutMargin"><strong>Course Highlights: </strong>This input field will allow you to select CMS Pages. From the CMS pages selected, the main image and the text within the abstract field are used to populate the main body area of the Academic Home  page. The following list contains compatible pages.</p>
<div class="level2">
