</div>
<br /> <img class="icon" height="20" src="Images/Internal_Use/Ingeniux_Training/Icons/list.png" width="20" />
<h3><strong>Facebook Integration: </strong></h3>
<div class="level1"><img class="icon" height="20" src="Images/Internal_Use/Ingeniux_Training/Icons/text.png" width="20" />
<p><strong>Facebook Integration Facebook ID#: </strong>Place a facebook ID# here to display the most recent facebook messages in the right column of the Academic Home  page.</p>
<img class="icon" height="20" src="Images/Internal_Use/Ingeniux_Training/Icons/text.png" width="20" />
<p><strong>Number of status messages to display: </strong>Enter the number of status messages you wish to display.</p>
<span class="clear"> </span></div>
<br /> <img class="icon" height="20" src="Images/Internal_Use/Ingeniux_Training/Icons/drop_down.png" width="20" />
